Introduction

Chic Angel was a two-member girl group under Liz Entertainment. They debuted on February 16, 2017 with the digital single "Is Love". In the later half of 2020, member Sia departed from the girl group. In June 2022, Xindy was added to the group. The group is assumed to have disbanded in early 2025.
